CygUtils
========================================================================
The cygutils package contains a collection of simple utilities from
various sources.

Runtime requirements (these, or newer)
  cygwin-1.7.5-
  libintl8-0.17-11
  libiconv2-1.13.1-1
  libpopt0-1.6.4-4
  libgcc1-4.3.4-3
  libstdc++6-4.3.4-3

Build requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.5-1
  cygport-0.9.85-1
  popt-1.6.4-4
  libpopt0-1.6.4-4
  gettext-0.17-11
  gettext-devel-0.17-11
  libgettextpo0-0.17-11
  libintl8-0.17-11
  libiconv-1.13.1-1
  libiconv2-1.13-10
  gcc4-core-4.3.4-3
  gcc4-g++-4.3.4-3
  libgcc1-4.3.4-3
  libstdc++6-4.3.4-3
  binutils-2.20.51-1
  autoconf-8-1
  autoconf2.5-2.65-1
  automake-4-1
  automake1.11-1.11.1-1
  cvs-1.12.13-10 (for gettext/autopoint)
  xz-4.999.9beta-11 (for lzma)
